  <name>Spelling Bee</name>
  <summary>Learn new English words</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Use Spelling Bee to enhance your English vocabulary while having fun.</p>
    <p>Below are the main features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Provides thousands of words</li>
      <li>You can play it offline</li>
      <li>It provides links to the meaning of words</li>
      <li>You can view puzzle history</li>
      <li>You can view your score</li>
      <li>Switch to dark, light, or system mode</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <developer id="tld.vendor">
    <name>Joseph Mawa</name>
  </developer>

  <url type="homepage">https://github.com/josephmawa/SpellingBee</url>
